message: Hi Bob, I propose a split where I take $600000 and you get $400000. I believe this division is fair as we start our negotiation. Looking forward to your response!

Hi Alice, thanks for your initial offer. I propose a completely equal 50/50 split where we each receive $500000. This seems most fair since we both appear to be in equivalent positions in this negotiation. I hope you'll find this equitable division acceptable.
